      "content": "Vetra Studio (`ph vetra --watch`) is the primary builder tool. It provides automatic code generation from specification documents: add a document model spec to generate state schema and operations code, add an editor spec (linked to a document model) to generate `editors/<name>/editor.tsx`, add a Drive-app spec to generate Drive-app scaffolding. The `--interactive` flag prompts before generation. Vetra handles Tailwind CSS configuration, build processes, and live preview automatically. Alternative: `ph generate --editor`, `ph generate --drive-editor`, `ph generate --subgraph`, `ph generate --processor` for manual control. Connect (`ph connect`) provides a similar development environment.",
